zed and direct replacement strategy confirmed\n+- [x] PRE-VALIDATION: ontology syntax precheck completed before editing\n+- [x] RESEARCH: reference and chemistry checks documented in `RESEARCH.md`\n+- [x] TERM-SEARCH: confirmed target and replacement term stanzas, and searched for usages\n+- [x] DESIGN-PATTERNS: obsoletion pattern reviewed and documented in `DESIGN_PATTERNS.md`\n+- [x] EDITS: used `obo-checkout.pl` / `obo-checkin.pl` workflow via `terms/GO_0043713.obo`\n+- [x] RELATIONSHIPS: removed active axioms from obsolete term; no rewiring needed elsewhere\n+- [x] SPECIALIZED-EDITS: used obsoletion/reaction/chemical-entity considerations as relevant\n+- [x] METADATA: added issue tracker item and replacement metadata; preserved existing historical provenance\n+- [x] AUTOMATED-VALIDATION: `make travis_build` passed\n+- [x] REFERENCE-VALIDATION: validated `PMID:16957230`\n+- [x] CHANGES-COMMITTED: committed local change to `src/ontology/go-edit.obo` only\n\n","files":[{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","relativePath":"ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,5 @@\n+Obsoleted `GO:0043713` `(R)-2-hydroxyisocaproate dehydrogenase activity` and replaced it with `GO:0140175` `(2R)-2-hydroxyacid dehydrogenase (NAD+) activity`.\n+\n+This was a straightforward direct replacement: the older term had no direct annotations, no internal GO usages, and its chemistry is covered by the broader EC/RHEA-backed replacement term.\n+\n+Changes committed in PR #<NN>.\n","additions":5,"deletions":0},{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md","relativePath":"PR_COMMENTS.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENT